

	 
      the passion is a movie that you will either love or hate. i really dont think you can be in the middle. i could be wrong. if you dont know the story of jesus, read it before you go, otherwise you will have no idea what is happening and mostly why it is happening. i cried from the time they whipped him until the end. if i wasnt crying, i was shaking. i want to see it again. that movie makes you think about how Jesus did that for me, for us. He went through the worst pain you can think of just so we can go to heaven and be with him. i dont really know how to put into words the feelings i had because they were so .. amazing. 
     

    
